overview:
Nathaniel Bailey is and Online Marketing Developer for a web design company (TME Solutions) based in Maidstone Kent. Nathaniel has been working for TME since 2008 and manages a number of e-commerce clients in a different niches from leisure products to minibus hire.

Along with working in the SEO industry Nathaniel also runs a number of established websites for different products, services and blogs including - but not limited to - guestbloger.com, gothis-store.co.uk, gameserverslive.co.uk, seotoolpack.com and others.

Nathaniel has always been interested in building developing and marketing/seo’ing websites for both business clients and his personal sites.

Due to having a large passion in the world of search engine optimisation and web development, Nathaniel’s skills in this market have excelled in many ways to give his works and private clients quality results on google and many other platforms.
